title: F Them Kids (Eboni K Williams Interview)
itunes:title: F Them Kids (Eboni K Williams Interview)
description:
Today on the show we had friend to the room Eboni K Williams, who spoke about her experience on RONY, wanting a family and living in her blackness. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a nurse that was suspended for joking about mistreating patients on tik tok and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
